cs.NI, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.CR 

This paper deals with relay selection in wireless networks, which is a topic related to networking and communication. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves information theory, which makes cs.IT (Information Theory) another likely category. The use of feedback and control in the relay selection process suggests that cs.SY (Systems and Control) could also be a relevant category. Additionally, the paper discusses the impact of varying parameters on performance, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) or cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
